casebody.data:
Irrera, Respondent, v. Hart, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

March 17, 1892.) Action by Paul Irrera against Hanna Hart.

Argued before Daly, C. J„ and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Goldfogle & Cohen, for appellant. Writ. H. Knox, for respondent.

Ho opinion. Motion to dismiss appeal denied, and appeal set over for May term.
